---
title: Quick Sweet and Sticky Beef with Green Beans and Pak Choi
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, this Quick Sweet and Sticky Beef has it all. Thai spices, hoisin sauce and teriyaki turn turn beef mince into a tasty topping for jasmine rice.
